{"tid":2510592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東涌映灣園11座950名居民檢測結果全屬陰性","createTime":"2021-04-30T09:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T09:41:02.000Z","uid":338154,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5614c3a59f0a218906211e8f7c7ce3f6095a36b6","tid":2510592,"uid":338154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:17:12.000Z","msg":"【17:09】食物及衞生局局長陳肇始、勞工及福利局局長羅致光、衞生署衞生防護中心總監林文健醫生、食環署副署長（環境衞生）黃淑嫻交代最新疫情情況。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始：居東涌映灣園11座的確診39歲外傭非近期來港，相信是從本地社區感染，是第一宗本地感染，涉及變種病毒的無源頭個案，反映有隱性傳播鏈。政府就其所住的大廈「封區檢測」，昨日約950名居民檢測結果全屬陰性。<br />\n<br />\n０１唔貼ＬＩＮＫ"},{"pid":"835066c486fd39c89a3dc1c63218f7f6e053b9c8","tid":2510592,"uid":68689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"正苦：坐21日啦仆街"},{"pid":"f0b5f7638fe57c25be1942d3091306d41db0530f","tid":2510592,"uid":90585,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:19:15.000Z","msg":"一早都知爆唔起架喇 恐懼撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c06f6794ef3af71c7b34d12bc828b8bfce35a4f","tid":2510592,"uid":338154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"835066c486fd39c89a3dc1c63218f7f6e053b9c8","tid":2510592,"uid":68689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"正苦：坐21日啦仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/door.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/door.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4dd5eff7d22e9e57cf05d08aa52da6d6d46088","tid":2510592,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"835066c486fd39c89a3dc1c63218f7f6e053b9c8","tid":2510592,"uid":68689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"正苦：坐21日啦仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" 